title: Pancheros Mexican Grill
typeOfFood: Lacto, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican, Tex-Mex, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Franchise quick-serve restaurant offering burritos, tacos, and salads, all of which can be made vegan by requesting no dairy, etc., and quesadillas which can be made vegetarian. Offers grilled veggies to be used in place of meat and has vegan tortillas and beans. Tortillas are fresh pressed to order, and the ingredients are mixed up before the burrito is rolled. Has Wi-Fi.
